pageContext.claim: “‘One of the most disgraceful examples of an abuse of power by a government official…when you read this report…this is a systematic effort to go after Candidate Trump, President Elect-Trump, and President Trump....you could virtually call this an attempted coup.’ @RepPeteKing”
pageContext.analysis: It's ridiculous to claim there was a coup attempt. The FBI and special counsel investigation into Trump's campaign and Russian election interference was upheld as legal by various judges. Special counsel Robert Mueller documented several instances of Trump potentially obstructing justice during the probe.
